Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,快起來 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.42,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要 放開我
